message.content: cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.NE. The paper deals with visual question answering, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. The use of hyper-dimensional computing also suggests a focus on machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely as well. Finally, the differentiable nature of the system implies the use of neural networks, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
